import React from 'react'; const RecipeCard = ({ recipe, onClick }) => { return (
{recipe.time}
{recipe.region}

{recipe.title}

{recipe.description}

{recipe.tags.slice(0, 2).map(tag => ( #{tag} ))} {recipe.tags.length > 2 && ( +{recipe.tags.length - 2} )}
{recipe.author.fullName}
{recipe.rating}
{recipe.likes}
); }; export default RecipeCard;
